history.content: I had previously asked Professor Sahai if EE16A would offer an alternate final, since the CS 170 final is at the same time as the EE16A final, and he told me that they would not be offering an alternate final. However, I just noticed that now Vladimir M. Stojanovic and Chunlei Liu are teaching EE16A, so I was wondering if the fact that the professors changed for the class may change the policy about alternate final exams? I emailed both professors but have not gotten responses yet, so I was wondering if anyone else happened to know whether EE16A will offer alternate finals. Thanks a lot!!!
history.subject: Does anyone know if EE16A will offer an alternate final?
